data.Name: Ross from Friends
data.Bio: Felix Clary Weatherall a.k.a., Ross From Friends is an electronic music producer specialising in his own fine-tuned brand of Techno and House. Hailing from Colchester, Essex, Ross From Friends has had continued support from the likes of Soundplate, BackTheTooFuture and Eton Messy to name a few. Read more on Last.fm
